 A Sunday Sun report claimed that Cassper has allegedly been spotted spending lots of time with a woman known as Thobeka Majozi.The tabloid also claimed that the rapper and Thobeka were apparently seen out on a date at one of Joburg s trendy restaurants together.Both Cassper and Thobeka have been silent on the rumours but if there is any truth to them it s evident why Thobeka caught the rapper s eye.She s sophisticated smart and sexy!